After more than two weeks of scintillating football at the TotalEnergies African Nations Championship (CHAN) 2022 in Algeria, four teams will now battle for victory.           Algeria will face Niger in the first semi-final at the Miloud Hadefi Stadium in Oran on Tuesday, January 31, 2023 at 1600GMT before Senegal face Madagascar at the Nelson Mandela Stadium in Baraki, Algiers on the same day at 1900GMT.